    <div class="container">
        <div class="label">Bankruptcy Court Index</div>
        <h1>United States Bankruptcy Court for the District of Connecticut</h1>
        <p>United States Bankruptcy Court for the District of Connecticut is one of the US federal bankruptcy courts whose public, RECAP-archived dockets are indexed here. The Open Bankruptcy Project maintains this national case-level index for empirical research and public-records access. Every case below links to the full docket on the Free Law Project&#x27;s CourtListener.</p>
    </div>
</header>

